The '''Norway national football team''' ({{langx|no|Norges herrelandslag i fotball}}, or informally ''Landslaget'') represents [[Norway]] in men's international [[Association football|football]], and is controlled by the [[Norwegian Football Federation]], the governing body for [[football in Norway]]. Norway's home ground is [[Ullevaal Stadion]] in [[Oslo]], and their head coach is [[Ståle Solbakken]]. Norway has participated in the [[FIFA World Cup]] four times ([[1938 FIFA World Cup|1938]], [[1994 FIFA World Cup|1994]], [[1998 FIFA World Cup|1998]] and [[2026 FIFA World Cup|2026]]), and once in the [[UEFA European Championship]] ([[UEFA Euro 2000|2000]]).

Norway is one of only three national teams with a winning record against [[Brazil national football team|Brazil]], and the only team to never have lost against them, with two wins and two draws in four matches, including a [[1998 FIFA World Cup Group A|1998 World Cup group stage match]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.11v11.com/teams/norway/tab/opposingTeams/opposition/Brazil/|title=Norway national football team: record v Brazil|website=11v11.com|publisher=11v11|access-date=11 December 2018|archive-date=14 December 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181214071008/https://www.11v11.com/teams/norway/tab/opposingTeams/opposition/Brazil/|url-status=live}}</ref>

After Euro 2000, Norway missed the next twelve major tournaments, until they qualified for the [[2026 FIFA World Cup]].<ref>{{Cite web |date=2023-11-19 |title=Erling Haaland to miss out on Euro 2024! How Norway have messed up qualifying for another major tournament |url=https://www.goal.com/en-gh/lists/erling-haaland-miss-euro-2024-norway-messed-qualifying/blt01be77dfd103af43 |access-date=2024-02-05 |website=www.goal.com |language=en-GH}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |date=2023-12-02 |title=Why Erling Haaland isn't at the Euros: How Man City star, Martin Odegaard missed out with Norway |url=https://www.sportingnews.com/us/soccer/news/erling-haaland-euros-man-city-martin-odegaard-norway/a4251d495a6588308a015cb5 |access-date=2024-02-05 |website=www.sportingnews.com |language=en-us}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |date=2023-02-13 |title=Can Haaland and Odegaard take Norway back to international prominence? |url=https://www.france24.com/en/live-news/20230213-can-haaland-and-odegaard-take-norway-back-to-international-prominence |access-date=2024-02-05 |website=France 24 |language=en}}</ref>